staging:iio:ad2s90: Add IIO_CHAN_INFO_SCALE to channel spec and read_raw

This patch adds the IIO_CHAN_INFO_SCALE mask to ad2s90_chan and
implements the relative read behavior at ad2s90_read_raw.

